						<div class="postbody">The attribute table assigns one of the four 4-color palettes to the tiles in the nametable.  It's difficult to explain in words the pattern in how this is done --- a diagram is pretty much a necessity -- and any diagram I could draw would be no better than the many diagrams already in existence.
<br />
<br />For this one... pick up a copy of nestech.txt, or look on the wiki, or look at some other nes technical reference and search the doc for "attribute tables" until you find the relevent info.</div>

